item.description:
Hi Trailblazers! Come join us for a lively dance with "Live Music, Friendly Dancers and Lots of Energy". No experience necessary. If you want a good workout and you want to meet some new friends, come to the Dover dance. It's a great dance with lots of helpful dancers to teach the new dancers the dances. Dances are "called" or instructed so you will be able to learn the dances.
I missed the dance last month and was told it was a huge crowd.
Bring soft soled shoes, water and your dancing feet!
I hope to see some Trailblazers there!
$7 admission.
See you there!
Peter
item.how_to_find_us: Ask for Marie - I'll be dancing!
